        <section id="Description">
            <title>Description</title>
            <p>CXF is a merging of the Objectweb Celtix project and the Codehaus XFire 
			   project. The goal is to combine the best concepts from the two projects and create 
			   an enterprise quality framework work for creating services. CXF will allow 
			   developers to use a variety of programming models, including JAX-WS, POJO, and 
			   Javascript, to develop services. The resulting services will have a pluggable 
			   binding and transport mechanism which enables a service to use more than 
			   SOAP/HTTP.</p>
        </section>
